---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<div class="max-w-screen-xl shadow-2xl mx-auto flex-1 font-serif text-slate-900" style="background-color: #f6f2ea;">
		
		<!-- Sticky Navigation -->
		<div class="sticky top-0 z-50 px-6 py-4" style="background-color: #FBF9F4; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
			<div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
				<nav class="flex items-center gap-8 text-sm">
					<a href="#library" class="flex items-center gap-2 hover:opacity-75 transition-opacity duration-200" style="color: #b08a30;">
						<span>📚</span>
						<span class="font-medium">The Library</span>
					</a>
					<span class="text-gray-300">|</span>
					<a href="#guides" class="flex items-center gap-2 hover:opacity-75 transition-opacity duration-200" style="color: #6f7f53;">
						<span>📘</span>
						<span class="font-medium">Guides</span>
					</a>
					<span class="text-gray-300">|</span>
					<a href="#tools" class="flex items-center gap-2 hover:opacity-75 transition-opacity duration-200" style="color: #2f4858;">
						<span>🧮</span>
						<span class="font-medium">Financial Tools</span>
					</a>
				</nav>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Header Section -->
		<section class="py-16" style="background-color: #FBF9F4;">
			<div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl">
				<h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-8 victoria-font" style="color: #2F4858;">
					Resources
				</h1>
				<div class="max-w-4xl">
					<p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
						A curated collection of books, guides, and tools to help you understand and apply the timeless principles of wealth creation. From historical insights to practical calculators, everything you need to navigate your financial journey with historical wisdom.
					</p>
					<p class="text-slate-600">
						Each resource has been carefully selected for its ability to illuminate the patterns that have governed prosperity across cultures and centuries.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- The Library Section -->
		<section id="library" class="py-20" style="background-color: #f6f2ea; border-top: 4px solid #b08a30;">
			<div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl">
				<h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-8 victoria-font" style="color: #b08a30;">
					The Library
				</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
					Curated books that shaped our understanding of wealth, markets, and human nature across centuries. These are the foundational texts that reveal the patterns behind great fortunes.
				</p>
				
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
					<div class="p-6 rounded-lg border-2 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200" style="background-color: #FBF9F4; border-color: #c9a34a;">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 victoria-font" style="color: #b08a30;">
							Historical Finance
						</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
							Classic works on the development of banking, markets, and wealth creation throughout history.
						</p>
						<ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-1">
							<li>• "The Ascent of Money" - Niall Ferguson</li>
							<li>• "A Monetary History" - Friedman & Schwartz</li>
							<li>• "The House of Rothschild" - Niall Ferguson</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					
					<div class="p-6 rounded-lg border-2 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200" style="background-color: #FBF9F4; border-color: #c9a34a;">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 victoria-font" style="color: #b08a30;">
							Wealth Psychology
						</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
							Understanding the mindset and behaviors that create and preserve wealth across generations.
						</p>
						<ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-1">
							<li>• "The Millionaire Mind" - Thomas Stanley</li>
							<li>• "Rich Dad Poor Dad" - Robert Kiyosaki</li>
							<li>• "The Intelligent Investor" - Benjamin Graham</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					
					<div class="p-6 rounded-lg border-2 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200" style="background-color: #FBF9F4; border-color: #c9a34a;">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 victoria-font" style="color: #b08a30;">
							Economic History
						</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
							Comprehensive studies on how economies and financial systems have evolved over time.
						</p>
						<ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-1">
							<li>• "The Wealth of Nations" - Adam Smith</li>
							<li>• "Capital" - Thomas Piketty</li>
							<li>• "Debt: The First 5,000 Years" - David Graeber</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- The Manual Section -->
		<section id="guides" class="py-20" style="background-color: #FBF9F4; border-top: 4px solid #6f7f53;">
			<div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl">
				<h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-8 victoria-font" style="color: #6f7f53;">
					The Manual
				</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
					Practical, actionable guides to help you navigate modern financial decisions with historical wisdom. These step-by-step manuals translate timeless principles into today's context.
				</p>
				
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
					<div class="p-8 rounded-lg border-2 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200" style="background-color: #f6f2ea; border-color: #6f7f53;">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-sm mb-6 flex items-center justify-center"
							 style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6f7f53, #4f5a2e);">
							<span class="text-white text-xl">💳</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 victoria-font" style="color: #6f7f53;">
							Credit Card Strategy
						</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
							How to leverage credit responsibly, build credit history, and maximize rewards—lessons from centuries of credit and debt management.
						</p>
						<span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #4f5a2e;">Coming Soon</span>
					</div>

					<div class="p-8 rounded-lg border-2 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200" style="background-color: #f6f2ea; border-color: #6f7f53;">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-sm mb-6 flex items-center justify-center"
							 style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6f7f53, #4f5a2e);">
							<span class="text-white text-xl">📊</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 victoria-font" style="color: #6f7f53;">
							Budgeting Frameworks
						</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
							Time-tested approaches to managing money, from ancient household ledgers to modern zero-based budgeting techniques.
						</p>
						<span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #4f5a2e;">Coming Soon</span>
					</div>

					<div class="p-8 rounded-lg border-2 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200" style="background-color: #f6f2ea; border-color: #6f7f53;">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-sm mb-6 flex items-center justify-center"
							 style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6f7f53, #4f5a2e);">
							<span class="text-white text-xl">🏠</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 victoria-font" style="color: #6f7f53;">
							Real Estate Investing
						</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
							From Roman villa investments to modern REITs—understanding property as a wealth-building tool across millennia.
						</p>
						<span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #4f5a2e;">Coming Soon</span>
					</div>

					<div class="p-8 rounded-lg border-2 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200" style="background-color: #f6f2ea; border-color: #6f7f53;">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-sm mb-6 flex items-center justify-center"
							 style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6f7f53, #4f5a2e);">
							<span class="text-white text-xl">💰</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 victoria-font" style="color: #6f7f53;">
							Emergency Fund Planning
						</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
							Building financial resilience—how merchants, nobility, and modern families have prepared for uncertainty.
						</p>
						<span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #4f5a2e;">Coming Soon</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Financial Tools Section -->
		<section id="tools" class="py-20" style="background-color: #f6f2ea; border-top: 4px solid #2f4858;">
			<div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl">
				<h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-8 victoria-font" style="color: #2f4858;">
					Financial Tools
				</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
					Calculators and planning tools to help you apply historical wealth principles to your modern financial decisions. Each tool is designed with lessons learned from centuries of wealth management.
				</p>
				
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
					<!-- Retirement Calculator - Active -->
					<div class="p-6 rounded-lg border-2 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200" style="background-color: #FBF9F4; border-color: #2f4858;">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-sm mb-4 flex items-center justify-center"
							 style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2f4858, #1f3442);">
							<span class="text-white text-xl">🏖️</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 victoria-font" style="color: #2f4858;">
							Retirement Calculator
						</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
							Calculate how much you need to save to achieve your retirement income goals.
						</p>
						<a href="/calculators/retirement" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-sm text-white text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 border border-transparent hover:border-white/20" 
						   style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2f4858, #1f3442);">
							Use Calculator →
						</a>
					</div>

					<!-- Coming Soon Tools -->
					<div class="p-6 rounded-lg border-2 opacity-60 hover:opacity-75 transition-all duration-200" style="background-color: #FBF9F4; border-color: #94a3b8;">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-sm mb-4 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-400">
							<span class="text-white text-xl">📈</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 victoria-font" style="color: #2f4858;">
							Compound Interest
						</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
							See how your investments can grow over time with compound interest.
						</p>
						<span class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400">Coming Soon</span>
					</div>

					<div class="p-6 rounded-lg border-2 opacity-60 hover:opacity-75 transition-all duration-200" style="background-color: #FBF9F4; border-color: #94a3b8;">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-sm mb-4 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-400">
							<span class="text-white text-xl">💰</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 victoria-font" style="color: #2f4858;">
							Historical Purchasing Power
						</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
							Compare the value of money across different historical periods.
						</p>
						<span class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400">Coming Soon</span>
					</div>

					<div class="p-6 rounded-lg border-2 opacity-60 hover:opacity-75 transition-all duration-200" style="background-color: #FBF9F4; border-color: #94a3b8;">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-sm mb-4 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-400">
							<span class="text-white text-xl">🏠</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 victoria-font" style="color: #2f4858;">
							Mortgage Calculator
						</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
							Calculate mortgage payments and compare different loan options.
						</p>
						<span class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400">Coming Soon</span>
					</div>

					<div class="p-6 rounded-lg border-2 opacity-60 hover:opacity-75 transition-all duration-200" style="background-color: #FBF9F4; border-color: #94a3b8;">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-sm mb-4 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-400">
							<span class="text-white text-xl">🛡️</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 victoria-font" style="color: #2f4858;">
							Emergency Fund
						</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
							Determine how much you should save for unexpected expenses.
						</p>
						<span class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400">Coming Soon</span>
					</div>

					<div class="p-6 rounded-lg border-2 opacity-60 hover:opacity-75 transition-all duration-200" style="background-color: #FBF9F4; border-color: #94a3b8;">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-sm mb-4 flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-400">
							<span class="text-white text-xl">📊</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 victoria-font" style="color: #2f4858;">
							Portfolio Allocation
						</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
							Optimize your investment portfolio based on historical data.
						</p>
						<span class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400">Coming Soon</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Newsletter CTA -->
		<section class="py-16" style="background-color: #FBF9F4;">
			<div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-2xl">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 victoria-font" style="color: #2F4858;">
					More resources coming soon
				</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-600 mb-8">
					Join our newsletter to be the first to know when new guides, tools, and reading recommendations are added.
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 max-w-md">
					<input
						type="email"
						placeholder="your@email.com"
						class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-sm border border-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-slate-400 focus:border-slate-400 transition-all duration-200"
					/>
					<button
						type="submit"
						class="px-8 py-3 font-semibold rounded-sm tracking-wide transition-all duration-200 border border-transparent hover:shadow-lg hover:border-white/20"
						style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2f4858, #1f3442); color: white;"
					>
						Subscribe
					</button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.victoria-font {
		font-family: 'Victoria', 'Times New Roman', serif;
	}
	
	/* Smooth scrolling for anchor links */
	html {
		scroll-behavior: smooth;
	}
	
	/* Add some offset for sticky nav */
	section[id] {
		scroll-margin-top: 80px;
	}
</style>